Package com.mashery.http

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HTTPHeader
    The interface identifies all the HTTP headers
    HTTPHeaderElementIterator
    Immutable iterator for header elements.
    HTTPHeaderElements
    Represents a structured header value consisting of name/value pairs with optional name/value parameters.
    HTTPHeaderIterator
    Immutable iterator for headers.
    HTTPHeaders
    Represents HTTP message headers as a parameter group with case-insensitive name lookup.
    MutableHTTPHeaderElementIterator
    Mutable iterator for header elements.
    MutableHTTPHeaderElements
    Represents mutable header elements.
    MutableHTTPHeaderIterator
    Mutable iterator for headers.
    MutableHTTPHeaders
    Represents mutable headers.
    MutableParamGroup
    Mutable parameter group.
    MutableParamIterator
    Mutable iterator for parameters.
    ParamGroup
    Immutable group of generic parameters (name/value pairs).
    ParamIterator
    Immutable parameter iterator where the elements are parameter names.

    MutableHTTPMessage
